但是一见如故，相逢恨晚！
But we hit it off right away!

192
00:17:13,541 --> 00:17:14,916
陈科
Chief Chen,

193
00:17:15,791 --> 00:17:17,291
陈科
Chief Chen,

194
00:17:17,833 --> 00:17:19,249
帮帮他吧
please help him.

195
00:17:19,291 --> 00:17:23,375
咦？这个花瓶是贵价货！
This vase must be expensive!

196
00:17:23,874 --> 00:17:25,583
小小意思
Just a modest gift.

197
00:17:25,833 --> 00:17:27,124
老规矩
Here's how it works:

198
00:17:27,166 --> 00:17:30,666
陈科玩腻了，就让回给张总！
when Chief Chen grows tired of it, Boss Zhang can buy it back!

199
00:17:30,750 --> 00:17:33,499
那至少值三十万！
It's worth at least RMB¥300K!

200
00:17:35,416 --> 00:17:37,375
不是说好了二十万吗？
Didn't we agree on RMB¥200K?

201
00:17:38,291 --> 00:17:39,874
我看错？
I got the price wrong?

202
00:17:40,541 --> 00:17:42,583
老猫烧须？
Oh, even Homer sometimes nods.

203
00:17:42,625 --> 00:17:43,791
怎会？
No way!

204
00:17:43,833 --> 00:17:47,041
说到古董，陈科才是专家
Chief Chen is a connoisseur.

205
00:17:47,083 --> 00:17:48,833
我们哪会懂，对吧？
What do we know?

206
00:17:48,874 --> 00:17:51,291
陈科说三十便三十
If Chief Chen says RMB¥300K, then it's RMB¥300K.

207
00:17:52,416 --> 00:17:54,291
明天上来工商局拿批文
Come get the business license tomorrow.

208
00:17:54,333 --> 00:17:57,625
我找个漂亮的框镶好给你
I'll have it nicely framed for you.

209
00:17:57,666 --> 00:17:58,833
谢谢陈科
Thanks so much, Chief Chen.

210
00:17:58,916 --> 00:18:00,625
好兄弟
We're buddies.

211
00:18:00,666 --> 00:18:03,416
张总，看看想吃什么？
Boss Zhang, what would you like to eat?

212
00:18:04,375 --> 00:18:06,458
咸菜扣肉
Braised pork with preserved vegetables.

213
00:18:07,458 --> 00:18:09,666
我才不吃肥腻的
That's too oily for me.

214
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,208
让我来点菜
Let me order.

215
00:18:13,458 --> 00:18:16,208
就吃鱼虾蟹海鲜餐，好吗？
Shall we have a seafood platter?

216
00:18:16,625 --> 00:18:18,000
我去叫
Let me order it.

217
00:18:18,041 --> 00:18:19,291
服务员！
Waiter!

218
00:18:19,333 --> 00:18:21,291
张总，祝你生意兴隆
Mr Zhang, best of luck with your business!

219
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:22,874
好，多谢
Thanks a lot.

220
00:18:23,458 --> 00:18:24,291
喝一杯
Cheers.

221
00:18:24,333 --> 00:18:24,958
干
Bottoms up!

222
00:18:25,375 --> 00:18:26,708
干！
Bottoms up!

223
00:18:36,541 --> 00:18:40,333
这一个，逢星期日，打高球，清水湾
This guy plays golf every Sunday in Clear Water Bay.

224
00:18:40,375 --> 00:18:45,583
单行路，够清静，电话有盲点，可以考虑
One-way road. Quiet. No phone signal. It may work.

225
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:47,416
饭还没到吗？
Hey! Where's our rice?

226
00:18:47,458 --> 00:18:48,666
下一个
Next.

227
00:18:49,499 --> 00:18:51,208
这个好办
This one is easy.

228
00:18:51,291 --> 00:18:53,375
超级玩家
A super playboy.

229
00:18:53,416 --> 00:18:55,833
每晚喝到天昏地暗
Drunk every night.

230
00:18:57,124 --> 00:18:59,874
最近还包养了小明星
He recently has an actress as a mistress.

231
00:19:02,874 --> 00:19:03,750
喂
Hey!

232
00:19:03,791 --> 00:19:04,625
饭呢？
Where is our rice?

233
00:19:04,708 --> 00:19:06,041
饭，稍等我一下
Rice? Give me a second.

234
00:19:06,083 --> 00:19:07,791
饭马上来，很快
Your rice is coming right away.

235
00:19:09,249 --> 00:19:11,124
有时候，司机会被支开
Sometimes he would send his driver away.

236
00:19:11,166 --> 00:19:13,208
不好意思，让你们久等
Sorry to keep you waiting.

237
00:19:13,291 --> 00:19:14,499
请慢用
Enjoy your food.

238
00:19:14,916 --> 00:19:16,166
关门
Close the door.

239
00:19:19,791 --> 00:19:21,708
先生，这边请
Sir, please follow me.

240
00:19:21,958 --> 00:19:23,166
给我一杯茶
Give me a cup of tea.

241
00:19:23,208 --> 00:19:24,666
喂！你刚不是去厕所吗？
Hey! Haven't you gone to the bathroom just now?

242
00:19:24,708 --> 00:19:26,499
﹣不要吐　　﹣饭是冷的！
- Wait! Don't puke.    - Hey! The rice is cold!

243
00:19:26,541 --> 00:19:27,583
你稍等我一下
Give me a second.

244
00:19:27,625 --> 00:19:29,083
﹣不好意思，饭是冷的吗？　　﹣我要茶！
- I'm sorry. The rice is cold?    - I want tea.

245
00:19:29,124 --> 00:19:30,583
﹣快点　　﹣小姐，麻烦你告诉我⋯
- Hurry up!    - Tell me the room number…

246
00:19:30,625 --> 00:19:32,750
﹣我要茶！　　﹣等我一下，我带你去
- I want tea.    - Give me a second. I'll show you the way.

247
00:19:32,791 --> 00:19:33,625
茶，我帮你拿
Sure, I'll get you tea.

248
00:19:33,708 --> 00:19:36,208
等一下，你们都等我一下，马上回来
Give me a second. I will be right back.

249
00:19:38,833 --> 00:19:40,750
将就一下吧
Take it easy.

250
00:19:40,791 --> 00:19:43,458
上来聊才能甩掉那些狗仔队
We came to China to shake off those cop dogs.

251
00:19:43,499 --> 00:19:44,583
你上次玩得那么大！
You went too far last time!

252
00:19:44,625 --> 00:19:46,916
要玩就玩大的
I live life to the full.

253
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:50,041
人生就这样
C'est la vie.

254
00:19:50,124 --> 00:19:51,750
不然怎么精彩？
There's no other way.

255
00:19:55,416 --> 00:20:00,000
我们之前偷车、爆窃、打劫运钞车
We've stolen cars, committed burglaries,

256
00:20:00,041 --> 00:20:01,416
一次比一次厉害！
and robbed cash vans.

257
00:20:02,416 --> 00:20:05,249
连大富翁都动了
We even kidnapped the tycoon's son.

258
00:20:05,291 --> 00:20:06,791
还绑架？
Should we do more kidnappings?

259
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:10,499
那你想到什么好主意？
What do you have in mind?

260
00:20:11,416 --> 00:20:13,458
说出来，我们商量一下
Spit it out. We can discuss.

261
00:20:37,041 --> 00:20:39,375
我是一个攀山运动员
I'm a mountaineer.

262
00:20:40,041 --> 00:20:41,708
我征服了一座山
After conquering one mountain,

263
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:45,375
当然得再找一座更高、更难爬的山
I need to find a higher and harder mountain.

264
00:20:46,291 --> 00:20:47,874
就这样
That's it.

265
00:20:50,583 --> 00:20:52,124
还没找到那座山
Before finding that mountain,

266
00:20:52,166 --> 00:20:54,041
先找钱吧
let's find the money first.

267
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:56,958
继续
Let's keep doing it.

268
00:20:58,166 --> 00:21:00,499
郑建权，五十三岁
Cheng, 53 years old.

269
00:21:00,541 --> 00:21:03,958
没儿没女，老婆当家
No children. His wife is in charge.

270
00:21:04,708 --> 00:21:08,249
以前一万多块钱一部，谁买得起？
A mobile phone used to cost over RMB¥10K. Who could afford that?

271
00:21:08,291 --> 00:21:10,958
你以为谁都是高干子弟？
Not everyone is a child of a high-ranking official.

272
00:21:12,541 --> 00:21:14,666
现在愈便宜愈好
Now the cheaper, the better.

273
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:18,375
我们一千万人口
We have a population of 10 million.

274
00:21:18,416 --> 00:21:20,874
你算算
Say RMB¥1K a set,

275
00:21:22,791 --> 00:21:25,249
对，一千块钱一部
RMB¥10K for 10 sets.

276
00:21:25,375 --> 00:21:29,000
十部就一万块，那时候就发过周润发了
We will be fatter than Chow Yun-fat!

277
00:21:30,083 --> 00:21:33,874
对，现在没人用传呼机了
Beepers are already outdated.

278
00:21:35,124 --> 00:21:39,708
好了，不说了，谈正事，一会儿再聊
OK, I'll talk to you later.

279
00:21:42,833 --> 00:21:45,291
潮哥，不好意思
Excuse me, Boss.

280
00:21:49,083 --> 00:21:50,499
继续讲吧
Please go on.

281
00:21:51,416 --> 00:21:54,874
你别难为小的了，小生意
Don't give us a hard time. We're doing small business.

282
00:21:54,916 --> 00:22:00,000
不说我的事了，潮哥，这帮小弟很棒
Big Bro, these kids are great.

283
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:02,666
走最前的老鬼在香港有案底
The guy who came in first has criminal record in Hong Kong.

284
00:22:02,708 --> 00:22:04,375
你带来有个屁用
Don't know why you brought him here.

285
00:22:05,083 --> 00:22:06,874
混蛋，叫你带些象样的来
I told you to bring some decent-looking guys.

286
00:22:06,916 --> 00:22:09,625
全都贼眉贼眼，都是蠢货
They all look like criminals and idiots.

287
00:22:10,166 --> 00:22:13,541
干你娘的，你该收山了
You should be out of business.

288
00:22:18,708 --> 00:22:20,249
他看什么？
What is he staring at?

289
00:22:24,083 --> 00:22:27,583
可是这个很聪明、很能干的
He is smart and helpful

290
00:22:30,083 --> 00:22:31,916
蓝衣那个也不要
I don't want the guy in blue either.

291
00:22:33,291 --> 00:22:35,166
这次两个就够了？
You only need two men this time?

292
00:22:36,083 --> 00:22:38,958
带他们去开开眼界嘛
Take the others to broaden their horizons.

293
00:22:44,666 --> 00:22:47,208
明白，完全明白
Got it!

294
00:22:47,416 --> 00:22:49,083
我去安排
Let me see to it.

295
00:22:50,916 --> 00:22:53,958
你看看看，他妈的看什么？
What are you fucking looking at?

296
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:56,499
走了，向阳、老胡
You, you, get lost!

297
00:22:56,541 --> 00:22:59,833
走了！别喝了！走了！
Stop drinking and scram!

298
00:22:59,874 --> 00:23:02,124
你们两个，跟我进来
You two come with me.

299
00:23:06,166 --> 00:23:07,958
快点了，快点了
Faster.

300
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:09,583
慢死了
So slow!

301
00:23:12,375 --> 00:23:13,666
潮哥
Big Bro Chiu,

302
00:23:13,708 --> 00:23:14,750
王磊
Wang Lei.

303
00:23:14,833 --> 00:23:16,083
红旗
Hong Qi.

304
00:23:16,124 --> 00:23:17,124
叫潮哥
Say Big Bro Chiu.

305
00:23:17,166 --> 00:23:18,083
潮哥！
Big Bro Chiu!

306
00:23:19,541 --> 00:23:20,458
听得懂广东话吧？
They understand Cantonese?

307
00:23:20,499 --> 00:23:23,375
懂，当然懂
Of course!

308
00:23:24,583 --> 00:23:27,499
来！先喝一杯
Come have a drink.

309
00:23:27,833 --> 00:23:29,249
装扮一下来香港见我
Spruce them up before sending them to Hong Kong.

310
00:23:29,291 --> 00:23:31,750
好，一定，我会的
Sure will!

311
00:23:46,291 --> 00:23:47,541
他妈的
Motherfucker.

312
00:23:47,583 --> 00:23:49,208
坐，吃饭
Sit and eat.

313
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,208
连长
Commander,

314
00:23:54,249 --> 00:23:56,041
这潮哥是什么来头？
who's this Big Bro Chiu?

315
00:23:57,375 --> 00:24:00,333
他就是不让你知道他什么来头
Who cares if he is Big Bro Chiu or not?

316
00:24:04,124 --> 00:24:05,666
他这个贱人
He is a douchebag.

317
00:24:05,708 --> 00:24:07,375
反正就是见一个人
He is a sly,

318
00:24:07,416 --> 00:24:09,499
就换一个名字的老狐狸
old fox who changes identities.

319
00:24:10,958 --> 00:24:14,625
跟他妈早年香港那个隐形贼王季正雄
He looks fucking like Kwai Ching-hung,

320
00:24:14,666 --> 00:24:16,458
一个他妈的样子
the invisible King of Thieves in Hong Kong.

321
00:24:17,291 --> 00:24:20,083
那个季正雄杀掉警察被通缉
Kwai Ching-hung disappeared

322
00:24:20,124 --> 00:24:21,708
就销声匿迹了
after killing cops.

323
00:24:21,791 --> 00:24:24,541
然后又蹦出个潮哥出来
Then Big Bro Chiu popped up.

324
00:24:24,583 --> 00:24:28,499
「潮哥」，不就是个名字而已
Big Bro Chiu is just a name.

325
00:24:50,083 --> 00:24:51,625
大辉在吗？
Is Fai here?

326
00:24:52,416 --> 00:24:53,958
阿辉
Fai.

327
00:24:54,833 --> 00:24:55,541
什么事？
What's up?

328
00:24:55,583 --> 00:24:57,249
﹣有人找你　　﹣喂
- Someone is looking for you.    - Hey.

329
00:24:59,499 --> 00:25:00,791
可乐哥
Bro Coke?

330
00:25:01,499 --> 00:25:02,291
喂
Hey!

331
00:25:02,333 --> 00:25:03,041
泰国人？
She's Thai?

332
00:25:03,083 --> 00:25:04,458
Noon，去买可乐
Noon, go buy a dozen Cokes.

333
00:25:04,541 --> 00:25:05,708
你什么时候回来的？
When did you come back?

334
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:06,958
刚刚回来
Just now.

335
00:25:07,708 --> 00:25:10,249
你干什么？这么客气，进来坐
You are too kind. Come in and have a seat.

336
00:25:10,291 --> 00:25:11,166
你说泰语吗？
Did you just speak Thai?

337
00:25:11,291 --> 00:25:13,416
难道我讲法语吗？
Do you think I speak French?

338
00:25:31,166 --> 00:25:32,333
好臭！
You stink!

339
00:25:32,375 --> 00:25:33,874
是吗？
Really?

340
00:25:34,083 --> 00:25:35,124
宝儿
Bo.

341
00:25:35,166 --> 00:25:36,833
你怎能这么没规矩？
How can you be so rude?

342
00:25:36,916 --> 00:25:38,708
进去帮爸爸开饭
Come help set the table.

343
00:25:39,249 --> 00:25:40,791
你坐一下，很快开饭
Dinner will be served soon.

344
00:25:41,583 --> 00:25:42,874
你真顽皮
Naughty girl.

345
00:25:43,166 --> 00:25:43,958
去洗手
Go wash your hands.

346
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,499
刚才洗过了
I did wash my hands.

347
00:25:46,249 --> 00:25:49,499
你昨天吃过饭，今天要不要吃？就是嘛
You ate yesterday. Are you going to eat today?

348
00:25:51,083 --> 00:25:53,833
慢慢来，宝儿，这么着急
Bo, slow down. Don't rush.

349
00:25:53,874 --> 00:25:55,291
可乐哥
Bro Coke.

350
00:25:57,583 --> 00:25:58,541
想喝吗？
You want some?

351
00:25:58,583 --> 00:26:00,375
我跟你一人一半吧
Shall we share it?

352
00:26:02,083 --> 00:26:03,000
别让她喝
Don't let her drink it.

353
00:26:03,041 --> 00:26:05,416
早前又咳嗽了，不然又要花钱看医生
She was coughing. I don't wanna spend money on meds.

354
00:26:05,458 --> 00:26:07,375
我没咳嗽，只是发烧而已
I wasn't coughing. I just had a fever.

355
00:26:07,416 --> 00:26:09,083
对，只是喝一点
It's all right to have a sip.

356
00:26:09,166 --> 00:26:11,166
什么没咳嗽？你就会顶嘴！
Not coughing? You are being cheeky!

357
00:26:11,208 --> 00:26:12,583
总之不能喝
I say no Coke.

358
00:26:19,958 --> 00:26:22,958
辉，我不吃，快要迟到
Fai, I'm not gonna eat. I'm running late.

359
00:26:24,208 --> 00:26:25,166
现在就出去？
You're going now?

360
00:26:25,291 --> 00:26:26,000
是的
Yes.

361
00:26:29,874 --> 00:26:31,833
乖乖的
Be a good girl.

362
00:26:34,916 --> 00:26:36,499
可乐哥，吃饭
Bro Coke, dig in.

363
00:26:37,333 --> 00:26:38,375
她不吃？
She's not eating with us?

364
00:26:38,416 --> 00:26:40,333
她去上夜班
She has to work night shift.

365
00:26:43,416 --> 00:26:45,333
她做按摩师的
She's a legit masseuse.

366
00:26:46,541 --> 00:26:48,083
吃块烧肉
Eat some barbecued pork.

367
00:26:48,416 --> 00:26:50,041
来，吃蔬菜
Bo, eat some veggies.

368
00:26:50,083 --> 00:26:51,708
经常不吃蔬菜
You seldom eat veggies.

369
00:26:54,041 --> 00:26:55,916
去不去海洋公园？
Shall we go to Ocean Park?

370
00:26:58,625 --> 00:27:00,375
玩过云霄飞车吗？想玩吗？
Shall we ride the roller coaster?

371
00:27:04,666 --> 00:27:08,208
我带你飞高一点，远一点，好吗？
Shall we fly higher and farther?

372
00:27:08,249 --> 00:27:12,291
不答我？搔你痒
Tickle, tickle.

373
00:27:16,791 --> 00:27:18,708
不要那么吵，要不然房东太太又骂人了
Stop making noise, or the landlady will be nasty.

374
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:20,958
她骂你没交房租吧
She's nasty because you haven't paid the rent.

375
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,458
还顶嘴，下来
You're being cheeky. Come down.

376
00:27:22,499 --> 00:27:25,166
厉害，臭丫头，敢跟老爸顶嘴
What a dragon lady, arguing with your father!

377
00:27:25,583 --> 00:27:28,499
这丫头，一玩就忘形了！穿好拖鞋
This girl plays too much! Wear your slippers.

378
00:27:28,541 --> 00:27:31,583
做好功课没有？快点，进去做功课
Have you finished your homework? Homework first.

379
00:27:31,625 --> 00:27:32,708
快点！
Quick!

380
00:27:34,166 --> 00:27:35,958
﹣我待会打你屁股　　﹣真乖
- I'll spank you.    - Good girl.

381
00:27:36,916 --> 00:27:38,791
这丫头！
This naughty girl!

382
00:27:41,291 --> 00:27:42,583
戒了
I've quit smoking.

383
00:27:42,958 --> 00:27:43,625
戒了？
Quit?

384
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:44,625
戒了
I've quit smoking.

385
00:27:44,666 --> 00:27:46,000
「嫖赌饮荡吹⋯
"Whoring, gambling, drinking, roaming…

386
00:27:46,083 --> 00:27:47,708
戒了不够帅」
and smoking are the hobbies of a king."

387
00:27:47,750 --> 00:27:49,291
是你说的
Your mantra.

388
00:27:52,208 --> 00:27:54,874
我要洗肾，不戒不行
I'm on dialysis. I have to quit.

389
00:27:55,916 --> 00:27:57,124
早就说你肾亏
Told you you're impotent.

390
00:27:57,166 --> 00:27:58,208
一蹲下就头晕
You feel dizzy when you squat.

391
00:27:58,249 --> 00:27:59,291
去！
Fuck!

392
00:28:00,791 --> 00:28:02,375
最近在干什么？
What have you been up to?

393
00:28:02,708 --> 00:28:04,375
我可以干什么？
What can I do?

394
00:28:04,458 --> 00:28:06,458
以前干地盘临时工
I used to do temporary construction work.

395
00:28:06,499 --> 00:28:07,750
现在全职带女儿
Now I'm a full-time babysitter.

396
00:28:07,791 --> 00:28:09,499
你呢？
What about you?

397
00:28:09,541 --> 00:28:10,541
我？
Me?

398
00:28:11,249 --> 00:28:13,375
我卖这个去大陆
I sell this in China.

399
00:28:14,708 --> 00:28:16,750
以后没有人用传呼机了
People won't use beepers anymore.

400
00:28:17,041 --> 00:28:18,833
将来大陆人一人一部
Every Chinese will own a mobile phone in the future.

401
00:28:18,874 --> 00:28:21,583
一部卖一千，十部一万
One sells for RMB¥1K, 10 for RMB¥10K.

402
00:28:21,625 --> 00:28:22,874
发过周润发
I'll be fatter than Chow Yun-fat.

403
00:28:22,958 --> 00:28:24,625
那么发？
Fat with loads of money?

404
00:28:25,124 --> 00:28:27,416
真厉害
Great.

405
00:28:30,333 --> 00:28:33,333
你真好，做老板了
You're doing great. You're becoming a boss.

406
00:28:34,916 --> 00:28:39,791
也对，走正路总比以前走偏门好
Going straight is better than going astray.

407
00:28:39,833 --> 00:28:42,708
我和你都不够狠，做不成大贼
We're not fierce enough to be Kings of Thieves.

408
00:28:42,750 --> 00:28:45,416
尽干些偷鸡摸狗的勾当
All we did were some petty crimes.

409
00:28:45,458 --> 00:28:49,625
生活没保障，觉也睡不好
Our life was insecure. We couldn't sleep well.

410
00:28:49,666 --> 00:28:53,124
又不是赚很多，也不知为了什么
And we didn't earn that much. So what's the point?

411
00:28:59,416 --> 00:29:01,208
我想在这里住几天
I'd like to stay here for a few days.

412
00:29:01,249 --> 00:29:01,958
什么？
What?

413
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,458
我睡沙发就可以
I can sleep on the couch.

414
00:29:04,791 --> 00:29:05,625
干什么？
What's that for?

415
00:29:05,666 --> 00:29:09,499
收下吧，帮补一下阿嫂
Take it. It will lessen your wife's burden.

416
00:29:10,916 --> 00:29:14,375
爸爸，手册不见了！
Dad, I can't find my school manual!

417
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,416
爸爸，爸爸
Dad, Dad.

418
00:29:16,458 --> 00:29:17,750
来了！
Coming!

419
00:29:19,708 --> 00:29:20,833
行了
That's fine

420
00:29:49,291 --> 00:29:52,416
(Jockey Club)

421
00:29:52,499 --> 00:29:55,249
番禺易发市场
Panyu Yi Fa Market

422
00:29:57,333 --> 00:29:59,791
三十部廿九吋新画皇，每部一万二
30 sets of 29-inch TVs. RMB¥12K apiece.

423
00:29:59,833 --> 00:30:02,416
另外八十部VCD机，每部四千
Plus 80 VCD players. RMB¥4K a piece.

424
00:30:02,541 --> 00:30:04,208
多谢你，六十八万
RMB¥680K, thank you.

425
00:30:07,249 --> 00:30:09,124
收了你七十万
You pay me RMB¥700K.

426
00:30:09,666 --> 00:30:10,874
货到通知你
I will notify you once the goods are delivered.

427
00:30:10,916 --> 00:30:12,041
下一个
Next.

428
00:30:12,124 --> 00:30:15,333
陈科的三十万，你点算一下
RMB¥30K for Chief Chen. Please count it.

429
00:30:17,833 --> 00:30:21,375
企业法人营业执照
Business License

430
00:30:33,333 --> 00:30:36,291
三十万，数目正确
RMB¥30K. The amount is correct.

431
00:30:37,375 --> 00:30:39,124
货到第一时间通知你
Will notify you once the goods are onboard.

432
00:30:41,249 --> 00:30:43,291
替我多谢陈科
Please extend my thanks to Chief Chen.

433
00:30:44,333 --> 00:30:47,874
我家的VCD机坏了
My VCD player is broken.

434
00:30:47,916 --> 00:30:49,958
送你一部新的，金
I'll give you a new one. Kam.

435
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:50,916
是
Yes.

436
00:30:52,499 --> 00:30:55,791
新款的三十三吋新画皇
The latest 33-inch TV set.

437
00:30:55,833 --> 00:30:57,208
好东西
Good stuff.

438
00:30:57,249 --> 00:30:58,583
也送给你吧
I'll give it to you, too.

439
00:30:58,625 --> 00:31:00,083
多谢张总
Thanks so much, Boss Zhang.

440
00:31:00,124 --> 00:31:01,166
不用客气
You're welcome.

441
00:31:02,874 --> 00:31:05,541
阿贵、阿广，拿部三十三吋新画皇
Gui, Guang, a 33-inch TV set and a VCD player.

442
00:31:05,583 --> 00:31:07,083
还有一部VCD机
Gui, Guang, a 33-inch TV set and a VCD player.

443
00:31:07,124 --> 00:31:08,458
好
Sure.

444
00:31:09,625 --> 00:31:12,333
大宝电器
Da-bao Electronics

445
00:31:13,958 --> 00:31:15,791
贪得无厌
She is greedy.

446
00:31:16,541 --> 00:31:18,333
做生意便是这样了
That's business.

447
00:31:18,583 --> 00:31:20,625
别整天摆副臭脸
Don't pull a long face all day long.

448
00:31:20,708 --> 00:31:22,333
张总！张总！
Boss Zhang, Boss Zhang.

449
00:31:22,375 --> 00:31:24,750
放心，他们俩会搞定
No worries. They will take care of it.

450
00:31:24,833 --> 00:31:26,333
﹣快点　　﹣什么事？
- Quick    - What's wrong?

451
00:31:26,541 --> 00:31:28,249
张总
Boss Zhang.

452
00:31:28,333 --> 00:31:29,708
什么事？
What's wrong?

453
00:31:33,208 --> 00:31:34,166
货物出事了？
Something wrong with the goods?

454
00:31:34,208 --> 00:31:36,166
不是，关门
No, close the door.

455
00:31:36,208 --> 00:31:37,833
关门
Close the door.

456
00:31:43,083 --> 00:31:47,541
嘴这么硬？打给你老婆报平安
Want to play tough guy? Call your wife now.

457
00:31:57,874 --> 00:31:59,458
打给你老婆
Call your wife now.

458
00:31:59,750 --> 00:32:01,000
报平安，混蛋
Tell your folks you're OK, asshole.

459
00:32:01,041 --> 00:32:03,124
打死我，你一分钱也拿不到
If you kill me, you won't get a cent.

460
00:32:03,166 --> 00:32:04,791
敢唬弄我？
Are you threatening me?

461
00:32:09,041 --> 00:32:10,874
卓，耐心点
Cheuk, be patient.

462
00:32:10,916 --> 00:32:13,333
他再不说，就断他粮水吧
If he doesn't talk, don't give him food or water.

463
00:32:20,458 --> 00:32:22,833
你好吵
You're so noisy.

464
00:32:23,583 --> 00:32:25,458
喂，干什么？
Hey, what are you doing?

465
00:32:25,499 --> 00:32:27,541
捡他上来，捡上来！
Get him back! Get him back!

466
00:32:27,958 --> 00:32:30,083
这里是金宝珠宝金行
This is the gold shop.

467
00:32:30,124 --> 00:32:32,166
平常会有一辆警车在门口
Usually there's a police wagon at the entrance.

468
00:32:32,208 --> 00:32:34,083
对面街有马会
Jockey Club is across the street.

469
00:32:34,124 --> 00:32:36,291
我们在里面看紧
We keep a close eye on the police wagon.

470
00:32:36,333 --> 00:32:40,249
待八时警车离去，我们立刻动手
As soon as it leaves at 8 PM, we rob the gold shop right away.

471
00:32:40,750 --> 00:32:43,249
那天跑夜马，会有好多人，搞定之后⋯
It's the racing night. It will be crowded. After it's done…

472
00:32:43,291 --> 00:32:45,541
﹣赚不了钱！　　﹣记得要跟紧我
- There's not much money in this.    - Follow me closely.

473
00:32:47,041 --> 00:32:48,166
你刚说什么？
What did you just say?

474
00:32:50,333 --> 00:32:52,416
你们做大茶饭的
You've committed big crimes.

475
00:32:52,541 --> 00:32:55,166
怎么就打劫小金行？
Why pick this small gold shop?

476
00:32:55,208 --> 00:32:56,249
对啊
Yes,

477
00:32:56,291 --> 00:32:59,583
听人家说，你们三大贼王合作
I've heard the 3 Kings of Thieves would join forces.

478
00:32:59,791 --> 00:33:02,291
没几个亿，都有几千万了
At least millions of dollars will be involved.

479
00:33:03,083 --> 00:33:04,916
什么三大贼王？
What 3 Kings of Thieves?

480
00:33:05,666 --> 00:33:07,041
说吧！
Say it!

481
00:33:08,041 --> 00:33:11,625
欢哥，你是否真的重出江湖
Bro Foon, are you making a comeback?

482
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:14,249
跟卓子强、季正雄
This time with Cheuk Tze-keung and Kwai Ching-hung.

483
00:33:14,291 --> 00:33:18,874
三大贼王合作做大案？
The 3 Kings of Thieves are collaborating?

484
00:33:19,791 --> 00:33:22,166
有人看到你们三人在大陆见面
Someone has seen you three meeting in China.

485
00:33:23,625 --> 00:33:25,249
你从哪儿听回来的？
Where did you hear this?

486
00:33:25,958 --> 00:33:27,541
外面全这么说
Everyone is saying that.

487
00:33:27,791 --> 00:33:29,333
这你也信！
And you believe it?

488
00:33:29,375 --> 00:33:33,333
老大不是说过，拿枪混不到饭吃！
Didn't Big Bro say you couldn't make money by toting guns?

489
00:33:33,958 --> 00:33:35,000
如果我是季正雄
If I'm Kwai,

490
00:33:35,041 --> 00:33:36,375
就不用和你们一起吃盒饭
I don't have to eat lunch boxes with you.

491
00:33:38,166 --> 00:33:39,708
蠢货
Idiots.

492
00:33:42,166 --> 00:33:43,708
神经病
That's ridiculous!

493
00:33:43,958 --> 00:33:45,583
一个「砰！砰！砰！」
Yip is all noise and fury.

494
00:33:45,625 --> 00:33:47,291
一个鬼鬼祟祟
Kwai is hush and shush.

495
00:33:47,333 --> 00:33:49,541
三个风格不一样，搞什么？
We are so different. How can it work?

496
00:33:49,708 --> 00:33:51,750
跟我走私多些电器
Smuggle more goods with me.

497
00:33:51,791 --> 00:33:53,625
一起赚到笑！
Let's make more money together!

498
00:33:54,708 --> 00:33:55,916
收到
Got it.

499
00:33:56,041 --> 00:33:57,124
英明！
Brilliant!

500
00:33:57,166 --> 00:34:01,208
有时心痒，也想重拾枪杆
Sometimes I feel like toting my gun again.

501
00:34:01,249 --> 00:34:02,874
打劫！打劫！
Robbery! Robbery!

502
00:34:02,916 --> 00:34:04,000
多威风！
That's so cool!

503
00:34:04,041 --> 00:34:05,375
你这叫威风？
You call that cool?

504
00:34:05,874 --> 00:34:07,958
老大开AK才威风！
Big Bro wielding AK-47 is cool!

505
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:10,166
不是这样开
Not like this.

506
00:34:10,666 --> 00:34:12,166
AK后座力大
AK-47 recoil is powerful.

507
00:34:12,208 --> 00:34:13,458
不是托着
Don't hold it.

508
00:34:13,499 --> 00:34:14,583
而是按着
Press it.

509
00:34:14,625 --> 00:34:15,583
站稳马步
Stand firm.

510
00:34:15,625 --> 00:34:17,333
射他老子
Shoot the hell out of him.

511
00:34:27,083 --> 00:34:30,249
怎么了？跟就跟
What the fuck?! Join me

512
00:34:31,333 --> 00:34:33,291
不跟就回去吃屎
or go home and eat shit.

513
00:34:37,083 --> 00:34:39,666
潮哥，那⋯
Big Bro Chiu,

514
00:34:40,083 --> 00:34:43,708
我们打个小金行，能赚多少钱？
how much can we earn from robbing this gold shop?

515
00:34:50,625 --> 00:34:51,416
打不打电话？
You're calling or not?

516
00:34:51,458 --> 00:34:55,333
你们觉得，如果三大贼王合作
If the 3 Kings of Thieves join forces,

517
00:34:55,375 --> 00:34:57,166
就算开「鱼蛋档」
even if we open a fish ball stall together,

518
00:34:57,208 --> 00:34:59,583
也很轰动吧？
we will create a stir, right?

519
00:35:00,041 --> 00:35:02,000
起什么名字好呢？
What shall I call our stall?

520
00:35:02,041 --> 00:35:03,291
打不打电话？
Are you calling your family or not?

521
00:35:21,375 --> 00:35:23,041
不要睡！
Hey, wake up!

522
00:35:25,416 --> 00:35:26,625
金库？
Gold depository?

523
00:35:27,166 --> 00:35:28,416
马场？
Racecourse?

524
00:35:33,249 --> 00:35:35,208
绑架彭定康？
Kidnap Hong Kong Governor Chris Patten?

525
00:35:35,249 --> 00:35:37,124
鲁平？
The Head of Hong Kong and Macau Affairs, Lu Ping?

526
00:35:37,666 --> 00:35:38,874
不行
No way.

527
00:36:01,291 --> 00:36:02,333
搞什么？
What are you listening?

528
00:36:02,416 --> 00:36:04,458
四大天王同台演出
The 4 Heavenly Kings singing on stage together.

529
00:36:04,499 --> 00:36:05,791
唱什么歌？
What are they singing?

530
00:36:07,625 --> 00:36:09,833
唱什么也听不到，有什么好听？
I can't hear a thing. What's so good about it?

531
00:36:10,208 --> 00:36:12,166
四大天王破天荒第一次合唱
When the 4 Heavenly Kings sing together,

532
00:36:12,208 --> 00:36:14,124
唱什么也很厉害
it's terrific no matter what they sing.

533
00:36:16,249 --> 00:36:18,958
我要水，水！
Water, give me water.

534
00:36:19,249 --> 00:36:22,166
我肯打了，我打了
I will make the call.

535
00:36:34,458 --> 00:36:36,458
我丈夫怎么样？我求求你！
How's my husband? I beg you!

536
00:36:36,499 --> 00:36:38,833
他身体不好，别为难他
He's not in good health. Don't hurt him.

537
00:36:38,874 --> 00:36:42,291
你别以为我们很有钱，只是表面风光
We are not as loaded as it may seem.

538
00:36:42,375 --> 00:36:44,625
卓先生，你怎么才肯放过我丈夫？
Mr Cheuk, can you let my husband go?

539
00:36:44,666 --> 00:36:47,291
要不你开个价，我自己掏腰包⋯
Name a price. I'll pay you from my own pocket…

540
00:36:55,041 --> 00:36:56,166
喂？
Hello?

541
00:36:56,208 --> 00:36:59,333
要不这样，我有八千万现金
I have $80M in cash.

542
00:36:59,375 --> 00:37:00,666
全给你好吗？
Is it OK?

543
00:37:00,958 --> 00:37:02,375
就八千吧
$80M it is!

544
00:37:02,416 --> 00:37:04,375
给我找叶国欢、季正雄！
Find Yip and Kwai!

545
00:37:07,750 --> 00:37:08,499
搞什么？
What the hell?

546
00:37:08,541 --> 00:37:10,083
三大贼王破天荒第一次合作
The 3 Kings of Thieves join forces for the first time.

547
00:37:10,124 --> 00:37:12,249
搞什么都厉害！
It will be terrific no matter what we do!

548
00:37:12,541 --> 00:37:13,583
什么也没想到
You don't even have a plan yet,

549
00:37:13,666 --> 00:37:15,208
找两个通缉犯放在身边
and you want 2 wanted men around you?

550
00:37:15,249 --> 00:37:15,958
我一定能想到
You know I will

551
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,333
你知道我一定能想得到的！
come up with a plan!

552
00:37:17,833 --> 00:37:20,000
这座山，就是我要找的山
This is the mountain I'm looking for.

553
00:37:20,041 --> 00:37:22,124
喜玛拉雅山！
Himalaya!

554
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:52,249
吃宵夜？
Having night snack?

555
00:37:52,541 --> 00:37:53,458
冰箱有可乐
There's Coke in the fridge.

556
00:37:53,499 --> 00:37:55,208
行，自己来
OK, I'll get it myself.

557
00:38:08,458 --> 00:38:12,000
辉，你朋友要住到什么时候？
Fai, how long is your friend staying?

558
00:38:14,499 --> 00:38:16,291
三、四晚吧
3 or 4 nights.

559
00:38:16,625 --> 00:38:18,041
我们有个女儿
We have a daughter.

560
00:38:18,083 --> 00:38:19,874
突然家中多了个男人
I don't feel comfortable…

561
00:38:19,958 --> 00:38:21,916
不是很方便
with a guy suddenly staying with us.

562
00:38:22,874 --> 00:38:26,208
他做什么工作的？
What does he do?

563
00:38:27,791 --> 00:38:30,958
卖手提电话的
He sells mobile phones.

564
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,416
别说了
Don't worry.

565
00:38:32,916 --> 00:38:34,375
睡吧
Go to sleep.

566
00:38:34,416 --> 00:38:34,916
好的
OK.

567
00:38:34,958 --> 00:38:39,208
我缝好衣服就去睡觉
I'll go to bed after sewing.

568
00:38:45,375 --> 00:38:48,249
正在带客人过来，三分钟到
I will arrive with clients in 3 minutes.

569
00:38:48,416 --> 00:38:49,750
收到
Got it.

570
00:38:53,375 --> 00:38:57,124
阿贵、阿广，卸货，赶快！
Gui, Guang, unload the goods. Be quick.

571
00:39:15,458 --> 00:39:16,625
老大，出事了！
Big Bro, we have a situation!

572
00:39:16,666 --> 00:39:18,499
番禺海关
Panyu Customs!

573
00:39:19,874 --> 00:39:21,833
金，金！
Kam! Kam!

574
00:39:21,874 --> 00:39:23,375
阿忠，停车
Chung, pull over!

575
00:39:27,833 --> 00:39:29,625
你去那边看看
Take a look over there.

576
00:39:29,708 --> 00:39:31,083
你再到那边看一下
Take a look again over there.

577
00:39:32,791 --> 00:39:34,291
