01:31:26,166 --> 01:31:28,000
你好，先生请问几位？
Sir, have you reserved a table?

1166
01:31:28,041 --> 01:31:29,458
姓陈的，订了房
I booked a room under the name of Chen.

1167
01:31:29,583 --> 01:31:31,708
订了房，好，稍等一下
Give me a second.

1168
01:31:33,041 --> 01:31:36,208
陈先生！来，麻烦这边请
Mr Chen. Please follow me.

1169
01:31:36,625 --> 01:31:37,874
请跟我来
This way, please.

1170
01:31:37,916 --> 01:31:38,916
喂
Hey.

1171
01:31:38,958 --> 01:31:39,708
饭到了没？
Where is our rice?

1172
01:31:39,750 --> 01:31:40,874
饭，稍等我一下
Rice? Give me a second.

1173
01:31:41,083 --> 01:31:42,916
饭马上来，很快
Your rice is coming right away.

1174
01:31:45,416 --> 01:31:47,249
不好意思，让你们久等
Sorry to keep you waiting.

1175
01:31:47,333 --> 01:31:48,499
谢谢
Thank you.

1176
01:31:48,541 --> 01:31:50,000
请慢用
Enjoy your food.

1177
01:31:50,499 --> 01:31:52,208
陈先生，这边请
Mr Chen. This way, please.

1178
01:31:52,833 --> 01:31:55,291
喂！你刚不是去厕所吗？
Hey! Haven't you gone to the bathroom just now?

1179
01:31:55,375 --> 01:31:59,166
等等，不要吐，吐在这里
Wait! Don't puke!

1180
01:31:59,708 --> 01:32:01,874
来⋯没事吧？
Are you all right?

1181
01:32:02,000 --> 01:32:05,041
不是去了洗手间吗？怎么会在这里出现
I thought you went to the restroom. Why are you here?

1182
01:32:05,583 --> 01:32:06,874
不好意思，这边请
I'm sorry. This way, please.

1183
01:32:06,916 --> 01:32:08,208
今天真的比较忙一点
We are super busy today.

1184
01:32:08,249 --> 01:32:09,375
﹣喂　　﹣这边请
- Hey!    - This way, please.

1185
01:32:09,458 --> 01:32:10,958
饭是冷的！
The rice is cold!

1186
01:32:11,249 --> 01:32:12,249
稍等我一下
Give me a second.

1187
01:32:12,291 --> 01:32:13,916
﹣不好意思，饭是冷的吗？　　﹣我要茶！
- I'm sorry. The rice is cold?    - I want tea.

1188
01:32:13,958 --> 01:32:15,124
好，等我一下，我帮你换过
Give me a second. I'll give you another bowl.

1189
01:32:15,166 --> 01:32:16,583
﹣快！　　﹣小姐，你告诉我，我自己去找吧
- Quick!    - Tell me the room number. I'll look for it myself.

1190
01:32:16,625 --> 01:32:18,833
﹣我要茶！　　﹣我带你去，等我一下
- I want tea.    - Give me a second.

1191
01:32:18,874 --> 01:32:19,666
茶，我帮你拿
Sure I'll get you tea.

1192
01:32:19,708 --> 01:32:22,499
等一下，你们都等我一下，马上回来
Give me a second. I'll be right back.

1193
01:32:27,541 --> 01:32:29,750
我们不会忘记你们
We should not forget you.

1194
01:32:29,791 --> 01:32:33,208
我们会以最关切的目光
And we should watch with the closest interests

1195
01:32:33,291 --> 01:32:39,083
看着你们开展非凡的新时代
as you embark on this new era of your remarkable history.

